Images Showing Dumi Masilela Wounded Finally Produced Shocking Published: 08 August 2017 Written by Online Writer Share on Facebook View Comments It has been confirmed that actor Dumi Masilela spent the night fighting for his life in hospital after being shot during an attempted hijacking in Tembisa on Wednesday night. The Rhythm City actor was parked on a road in the area with a friend when they were approached by a black Jeep. They tried to flee but a chase ensued. &ldquo;They tried to drive off but the black Jeep followed and the occupants opened fire. He (Masilela) was shot in the upper body,&rdquo; police spokesperson Kay Makhubele said. His friend who was in the car with him rushed the actor to hospital where he spent the night fighting for his life. Officials confirmed he died this morning. The actor was married to Muvhango actress Simphiwe Ngema and the two had become media darlings as their romance blossomed. Images showing Dumi Masalela wounded and in pain have finally been produced by the police after the permission from Dumi&rsquo;s wife and family.Not for sensitive viewers : Source: Imzansi View the discussion thread. blog comments powered by DISQUS back to top Google Tweet Pin it Tweet Next